{"title":"造巨轮唱船歌","authors":["邢连明"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"造巨轮唱船歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连造船厂工人　邢连明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芝麻花开节节高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着东风红旗飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌好听俺来唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我造巨轮唱船歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出东方一片红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军万马齐出动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首创纪录万吨船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压倒英美和日本。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅开始登尖端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报频传我占先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马奔腾气势雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"废寝忘食干不停！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分秒不让抢时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了万吨立大功！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寸寸光阴寸寸金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下活儿怎安心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚霞飞来满天红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴滴汗珠金莹莹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道焊光是天灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老头小伙逞威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说我老？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活到共产主义有余零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上北斗有七星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船台星星密层层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初冬海风刺人寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横挥大锤扫北风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑天当白天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天等于二十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万吨巨轮飞天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗乘东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日行万里展鹏程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首笑望笨美英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的领导出英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄奇迹多无穷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任我嘴巧如百灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也难唱尽英雄颂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}